        "title": "refactor: split subagent delivery state",
        "body": "## Summary\n- Split subagent run bookkeeping into nested `execution`, `completion`, and `delivery` state, with legacy flat persisted fields normalized into the new shape and removed from the live run type.\n- Separated interrupted child execution resume from completion delivery: restart recovery now resumes only interrupted runs internally, while terminal completion notification uses durable delivery state.\n- Added backend-gated internal session effects plus private run transcripts so recovery/delivery model turns do not mutate visible `/status` or history, while still preserving recovered output for delivery.\n\n## Verification\n- `pnpm tsgo:core`\n- `node scripts/run-tsgo.mjs -p test/tsconfig/tsconfig.core.test.json --incremental --tsBuildInfoFile .artifacts/tsgo-cache/core-test.tsbuildinfo`\n- `git diff --check`\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/gateway/call.test.ts src/agents/subagent-orphan-recovery.test.ts src/agents/subagent-delivery-state.test.ts src/agents/internal-session-effects.test.ts src/agents/agent-command.live-model-switch.test.ts src/cron/isolated-agent/subagent-followup.test.ts src/agents/subagent-announce-output.test.ts src/agents/subagent-registry.steer-restart.test.ts --reporter=dot` (16 files / 444 tests)\n- `OPENCLAW_TESTBOX=1 pnpm check:changed` via Blacksmith Testbox `tbx_01ksbaqrtywwkqb72p3hr5g3at`\n- `autoreview helper --engine claude --mode local --prompt-file /tmp/delivery-refactor.md --no-tools --no-web-search --prompt 'Only report accepted/actionable findings in files changed by this local diff. Do not report findings against unchanged neighboring files; mention them only as non-blocking context if needed.'` (clean)\n\n## Real behavior proof\nBehavior addressed: Subagent restart recovery no longer uses parent-visible recovery-progress announcements or scattered flat delivery fields; interrupted child execution is resumed internally, terminal completion delivery is retried through durable delivery state, and internal runs do not mutate user-visible `/status` or history.\nReal environment tested: Local focused Vitest and type gates, plus Blacksmith Testbox delegated changed gate before final small review fixes.\nExact steps or command run after this patch: `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/gateway/call.test.ts src/agents/subagent-orphan-recovery.test.ts src/agents/subagent-delivery-state.test.ts src/agents/internal-session-effects.test.ts src/agents/agent-command.live-model-switch.test.ts src/cron/isolated-agent/subagent-followup.test.ts src/agents/subagent-announce-output.test.ts src/agents/subagent-registry.steer-restart.test.ts --reporter=dot`\nEvidence after fix: Focused runtime proof passed 16 files / 444 tests; `pnpm tsgo:core`, core-test tsgo, and `git diff --check` passed after the final commit contents.\nObserved result after fix: Recovery, delivery, internal-session, cron fallback, gateway guard, and steer-restart regressions completed successfully.\nWhat was not tested: Live gateway restart with an in-flight real provider subagent; later Testbox reruns hit checkout/no-merge-base infra after prior green Testbox proof.\n",
